article_title: Andy Barr and Elisabeth Jensen offer vastly different prescriptions for Kentucky's job woes
article_text: U.S. Rep. Andy Barr, R-Lexington, and Elisabeth Jensen, his Democratic challenger in the Nov. 4 election, agree that Congress must act to get more Kentuckians into good jobs. That's also where their agreement appears to end.
